    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While the interior is clean and the exterior paint retains a nice shine, you may find some minor cosmetic wear consistent with regular use, such as small stone chips or light interior scuffing. It is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
