      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer. Demonstrating consistent care and a comprehensive service history, it offers both refined performance and long-term dependability. Its current state reflects a high standard of ownership, ensuring a sophisticated driving experience and exceptional value for its next proprietor.",
      "price": 34500.0,
