    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and still drives like a dream\u2014perfect for anyone who needs a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look; I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 28900.0,
