      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, it represents a distinguished choice for the discerning driver seeking value without compromise. Experience the assurance of quality engineering in a package designed for longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
